snippet.title: Astro Bot - Winter Wonder Christmas Level Gameplay | All Bots
snippet.description: Astro Bot’s Christmas DLC is here, and with it comes a brand new stage called Winter Wonder. This stage is massive and features some never-before-seen bots. In this video, we’ll show you where to get every bot and controller!
